title: Get You in the Morning
text:
"Get You in the Morning" is a song by Canadian group Crash Test Dummies and was the second and final single from their 1999 album Give Yourself a Hand. This song is one of two songs to feature Ellen Reid on lead vocals.


== Track listing ==
Get You In The Morning [Radio Edit]
Party's Over
Get You In The Morning [Extended Remix]


== Music video ==
The music video for the song features Ellen Reid switching to various TV stations featuring the rest of the band doing various random acts.
